title: Unnamed earthwork in the Tebaga Gap
description: The so-called "Tebaga clausura", a Roman earthwork located northeast of Bezereos at Tebaga in Tunisia.

properties.description: Roman clausura between the Gebel Matmata and the Gebel Tebaga. Area of the gate.
